But now, when we say young ones, to whom are we referring?

00:00:23.070 --> 00:00:26.050
As evidence of Jehovah's love,

00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:30.010
some may immediately think of the animated series of videos

00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:37.109
entitled Become Jehovah's Friend Feaching Featuring Caleb and Sophia.

00:00:37.109 --> 00:00:45.810
And that has indeed been evidence of Jehovah's and the governing body's love for little children.

00:00:45.810 --> 00:00:49.609
