00:07:12.889 --> 00:07:24.720
In so many ways, Jehovah and his organization show their love and appreciation for all you dear young ones.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:27.959
What can you young ones do in return?

00:07:27.959 --> 00:07:32.560
You may say, I go to all the meetings and out in service.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.639
Well, that is wonderful.

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:41.000
