00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:56.800
But if you think about it, even more important is having a good personal relationship with Jehovah.

00:07:56.800 --> 00:08:01.879
In Luke chapter 10, verse 27, it says,

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:15.120
You must love Jehovah your God with your whole heart and with your whole soul and with your whole strength and with your whole mind.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:22.720
